{
  "video_id": "0F2hSqeLDQM",
  "title": "How does science fiction influence the real world? | The Economist",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15870.0,
      "end_time": 18070.0,
      "text": "If you're watching this on your phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18070.0,
      "end_time": 20393.0,
      "text": "it's partly thanks to Captain Kirk."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21610.0,
      "end_time": 25560.0,
      "text": "In Star Trek, first broadcast in 1966,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25560.0,
      "end_time": 29163.0,
      "text": "he used a pocket-sized device\nto communicate with his crew."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30390.0,
      "end_time": 34320.0,
      "text": "Martin Cooper, the man who\ninvented the mobile phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 34320.0,
      "end_time": 37530.0,
      "text": "says the show was the\ninspiration for his idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37530.0,
      "end_time": 39553.0,
      "text": "which launched seven years later."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40890.0,
      "end_time": 44740.0,
      "text": "Amazon founder Jeff Bezos based Alexa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44740.0,
      "end_time": 46740.0,
      "text": "the voice-activated speaker on"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46740.0,
      "end_time": 48980.0,
      "text": "Star Trek's talking computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48980.0,
      "end_time": 50870.0,
      "text": "Transporters engaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50870.0,
      "end_time": 51747.0,
      "text": "Welcome aboard."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52650.0,
      "end_time": 54930.0,
      "text": "Sci-fi fan Elon Musk"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54930.0,
      "end_time": 57750.0,
      "text": "is building rockets that\nhe hopes will one day"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57750.0,
      "end_time": 58993.0,
      "text": "carry people to Mars."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61420.0,
      "end_time": 65930.0,
      "text": "Submarines, helicopters,\nrockets, and touch screens"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65930.0,
      "end_time": 68300.0,
      "text": "all appeared in science fiction"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68300.0,
      "end_time": 70493.0,
      "text": "before becoming science fact."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71930.0,
      "end_time": 74893.0,
      "text": "Sci-fi inspires real world technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75740.0,
      "end_time": 78840.0,
      "text": "It also provides a way to\nexplore the moral dilemmas"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78840.0,
      "end_time": 81123.0,
      "text": "that advanced technologies could pose."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85200.0,
      "end_time": 89063.0,
      "text": "Paul McAuley is a scientist\nturned science fiction writer."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 93397.0,
      "end_time": 96480.0,
      "text": "All science fiction is\nbasically about is presence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96480.0,
      "end_time": 98750.0,
      "text": "so it's about a heightened\nversion of the present."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 98750.0,
      "end_time": 102300.0,
      "text": "It's about anticipating where\ntechnology is going to go"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 102300.0,
      "end_time": 104880.0,
      "text": "and it's about our fears of\nwhere technology is going to go"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 104880.0,
      "end_time": 109110.0,
      "text": "and what uses or misuses we\nmight make of that technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 110661.0,
      "end_time": 111680.0,
      "text": "Divers information paper's ready and--"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 111680.0,
      "end_time": 113360.0,
      "text": "Techno world, do you\nneed to buy a suitcase?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 113360.0,
      "end_time": 114193.0,
      "text": "Utopia, huh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 114193.0,
      "end_time": 115860.0,
      "text": "You know they set up shop here, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 116960.0,
      "end_time": 119590.0,
      "text": "Few films better encapsulate this than"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119590.0,
      "end_time": 123363.0,
      "text": "Ridley Scott's 1982 cult\nclassic Blade Runner."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 128370.0,
      "end_time": 131100.0,
      "text": "The film is set in a dystopian future"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 131100.0,
      "end_time": 134280.0,
      "text": "where synthetic human\nworkers are bio engineered"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 134280.0,
      "end_time": 135603.0,
      "text": "by a corporate power."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 138690.0,
      "end_time": 141500.0,
      "text": "In London, fans are\narriving for a Blade Runner"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 141500.0,
      "end_time": 143969.0,
      "text": "screening with a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 143969.0,
      "end_time": 145781.0,
      "text": "Keep moving, guys, come on."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 145781.0,
      "end_time": 146971.0,
      "text": "Let's go, quickly scan."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 152210.0,
      "end_time": 155360.0,
      "text": "We are in World Terminus, checkpoint 4.C"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 155360.0,
      "end_time": 158360.0,
      "text": "We're in Los Angeles in 2019."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 158360.0,
      "end_time": 161290.0,
      "text": "Secret Cinema is a multilayer\nphysical experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 161290.0,
      "end_time": 162860.0,
      "text": "We build these physical sets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 162860.0,
      "end_time": 165510.0,
      "text": "creating a world inspired by a film."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 165510.0,
      "end_time": 166960.0,
      "text": "So instead of just watching a film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166960.0,
      "end_time": 169850.0,
      "text": "you literally buy a ticket,\nyou become a character,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 169850.0,
      "end_time": 173360.0,
      "text": "and you become part of an\ninteractive theatrical experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 173360.0,
      "end_time": 174310.0,
      "text": "Hey you lot in there!"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174310.0,
      "end_time": 176220.0,
      "text": "You thirsty or what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176220.0,
      "end_time": 179160.0,
      "text": "I think the science fiction\ngenre allows us to dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 179160.0,
      "end_time": 180620.0,
      "text": "about another world."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180620.0,
      "end_time": 182590.0,
      "text": "We've taken the inspiration\nfrom Blade Runner"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182590.0,
      "end_time": 184633.0,
      "text": "and built an entire world around it."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 185630.0,
      "end_time": 187990.0,
      "text": "The film explores the ethical implications"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 187990.0,
      "end_time": 190330.0,
      "text": "of creating highly intelligent robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 190330.0,
      "end_time": 193453.0,
      "text": "that have thoughts,\nfeelings, and emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 196820.0,
      "end_time": 199480.0,
      "text": "My wife's just back from\na convention about AI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 199480.0,
      "end_time": 201650.0,
      "text": "artificial intelligence, in Cambridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 201650.0,
      "end_time": 204440.0,
      "text": "A lot of the AI people think\nabout what would happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 204440.0,
      "end_time": 206300.0,
      "text": "if real AI came on very powerfully"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 206300.0,
      "end_time": 208290.0,
      "text": "and what they'd do to us\nand that's one of the things"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208290.0,
      "end_time": 210300.0,
      "text": "that science fiction has been exploring"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 210300.0,
      "end_time": 211600.0,
      "text": "for quite a long time now."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 214250.0,
      "end_time": 216510.0,
      "text": "Steven Spielberg's latest movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216510.0,
      "end_time": 220540.0,
      "text": "Ready Player One, explores\nanother emerging technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 220540.0,
      "end_time": 221663.0,
      "text": "virtual reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 224170.0,
      "end_time": 227200.0,
      "text": "The film imagines a future\nwhere overpopulation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 227200.0,
      "end_time": 229660.0,
      "text": "pollution, and climate change have forced"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 229660.0,
      "end_time": 232923.0,
      "text": "most people to live in\nsprawling, slum-like cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 234170.0,
      "end_time": 237010.0,
      "text": "Young people escape the\ndesolation by living much"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 237010.0,
      "end_time": 239013.0,
      "text": "of their lives in virtual reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 239980.0,
      "end_time": 241305.0,
      "text": "Are you ready?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 245530.0,
      "end_time": 246900.0,
      "text": "Although there is a wide gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 246900.0,
      "end_time": 249530.0,
      "text": "between the virtual\nworld shown in the film"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 249530.0,
      "end_time": 252640.0,
      "text": "and the capabilities of\ncurrent VR technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 252640.0,
      "end_time": 254970.0,
      "text": "the idea that young people can get hooked"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 254970.0,
      "end_time": 258083.0,
      "text": "on virtual fantasies is\na long-standing concern."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 260790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261840.00000000003,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no!"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 264700.0,
      "end_time": 266730.0,
      "text": "To be compelling, science fiction"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 266730.0,
      "end_time": 268410.0,
      "text": "has to be convincing."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 268410.0,
      "end_time": 271090.0,
      "text": "So writers and film\ndirectors enlist the help of"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 271090.0,
      "end_time": 272983.0,
      "text": "designers and engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 273920.0,
      "end_time": 276500.0,
      "text": "Syd Mead designed the look\nof some of Hollywood's"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 276500.0,
      "end_time": 279140.0,
      "text": "most seminal sci-fi films including"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 279140.0,
      "end_time": 283410.0,
      "text": "Blade Runner, Star Trek The\nMotion Picture, and Aliens."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 283410.0,
      "end_time": 286560.0,
      "text": "In the real world, he's\ndesigned cars for Ford"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 286560.0,
      "end_time": 288580.0,
      "text": "and electronics for Philips."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 289590.0,
      "end_time": 291740.0,
      "text": "Because I'm a trained designer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 291740.0,
      "end_time": 295070.0,
      "text": "I can imagine how things might be made."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 295070.0,
      "end_time": 297860.0,
      "text": "People always say that my stuff looks real"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 297860.0,
      "end_time": 299690.0,
      "text": "even though it's futuristic."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 299690.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "The pods for Aliens that I designed were"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 304700.0,
      "text": "real mechanical articulations."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 304700.0,
      "end_time": 307240.0,
      "text": "When they opened, they\nlooked absolutely real"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 307240.0,
      "end_time": 310413.0,
      "text": "for people to be in for\nlong duration space travel."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 311490.0,
      "end_time": 315284.0,
      "text": "I was hired to design the\nvehicles for Blade Runner."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 315284.0,
      "end_time": 317980.0,
      "text": "Deckard's vehicle was, in my mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 317980.0,
      "end_time": 321083.0,
      "text": "a decommissioned aerial limousine."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 322290.0,
      "end_time": 325191.0,
      "text": "It's overlaying the\nfamiliar with the weird"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 325191.0,
      "end_time": 326940.0,
      "text": "and that's a surefire formula"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 326940.0,
      "end_time": 329023.0,
      "text": "for interesting things to look at."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 330410.0,
      "end_time": 332130.0,
      "text": "Science fiction introduces"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 332130.0,
      "end_time": 335750.0,
      "text": "people to real world\nscience and technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 335750.0,
      "end_time": 338800.0,
      "text": "Some fans develop a lifelong passion."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 338800.0,
      "end_time": 341170.0,
      "text": "The tech industry is led by sci-fi nerds"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 341170.0,
      "end_time": 343220.0,
      "text": "who are creating the\nthings they read about"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 343220.0,
      "end_time": 344710.0,
      "text": "or saw on screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 344710.0,
      "end_time": 347910.0,
      "text": "We all stand to benefit\nfrom their creations."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 347910.0,
      "end_time": 351310.0,
      "text": "Provided, that is, they can\navoid the ethical pitfalls"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 351310.0,
      "end_time": 353253.0,
      "text": "depicted in science fiction."
    }
  ]
}